            },
            "description": "TC-ITEMS-02: GET adaptation by ID\nBUG-008 (Major, P1): GetItemById(int id) — parameter is int, Entity.Id is Guid\n\nReal behavior per input type:\n  /api/items/1         → 500 (FindAsync(1) fails on Guid column)\n  /api/items/<guid>    → 400 (model binding: Guid cannot bind to int)\n  /api/items/<empty>   → 400 (missing route value)\n\nFix: change signature to GetItemById(Guid id)\n\nThis test uses integer '1' to trigger the 500 and document BUG-008."
          }
